1) Node version should be atleast v18.18.0
    if Not
        nvm install v18.18.0
        nvm use v18.18.0
2) npm create vite@latest ReactJS-Projects -- --template react
3) cd ReactJS-Projects
4) npm install
5) npm run dev


for React Router
npm install react-router-dom

for tailwind css(https://tailwindcss.com/docs/installation/using-vite)
npm install tailwindcss @tailwindcss/vite